{"word":"ἐλεφαίρομαι","slug":"ἐλεφαίρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n33636\" key=\"e)lefai/romai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐλεφαίρομαι</orth>, old <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Verb, perh. connected with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀλοφώϊος</foreign> (q. v.), <sense id=\"n33636.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cheat with empty hopes</tr_>, said of the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">false</tr_> dreams that come through the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ivory</tr_> gate (with play on <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐλέφας</foreign>, cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κραίνω</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, οἱ μέν κ᾽ ἔλθωσι διὰ πριστοῦ ἐλέφαντος, οἵ ῥ) ἐλεφαίρονται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:565\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.565</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cheat, overreach</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐλεφηράμενος . . Τυδεΐδην</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:388\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.388</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n33636.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of the Nemean lion, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐλεφαίρετο φῦλ᾽ ἀνθρώπων</foreign> he <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">used to destroy</tr_> them, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:330\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">330</biblScope></bibl>. (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram> </gramGrp> only in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author></bibl>, who also has <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 1</tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐλεφῆραι· ἀπατῆσαι</foreign>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}